snippet.title: Sunset Shores - Release and Trailer
snippet.description:
Sunset Shores is a brand new mini-mod of NSMB2 that replaces all of world 1 with a new sunset ascetic and 8 beach themed stages. Along with the new levels, the mod features a few new tunes and for the first time, some code modifications!

Download
http://smbnext.net/sunsetshores/

If you are interested in this type of mod, you should check out SMBNext. It's a full mod of NSMB2 that aims to bring in all sorts of cool new stuff. Come hang with us on our discord server https://discord.gg/A5QWV3g
